Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.55,0:00:07.28,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I have gathered you all here \Ntoday for one reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.28,0:00:09.42,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I want all of us to overcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.42,0:00:11.61,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,the grave situation afflicting \NSakura Hall together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.61,0:00:14.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The subject of this Sakura \NHall meeting is:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.83,0:00:17.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,the Shiina Mashiro-san sitting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:20.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This morning, by the time I'd\N helped her put on her socks,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:23.21,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and fix her bed hair, we were late...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:22.10,Saku-overlap,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}This is heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.10,0:00:23.21,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.21,0:00:25.17,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Shiina, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:25.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,On our way to school, we got lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.78,0:00:27.22,Saku-overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.78,0:00:27.99,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and finally arrived at school \Nhalfway through second period.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:30.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina's a little different,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.73,0:00:33.40,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,so she isn't capable of \Nleading a normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:36.68,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We should create a system where \Nwe take turns in looking after—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.51,0:00:40.43,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.43,0:00:42.35,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,"Notebook PC" and "no panties" \Nkinda sound similar, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:43.27,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you on about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:45.64,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Well, her parents did tell her...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.64,0:00:48.77,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that she needed someone \Nto look after her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:52.06,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we decided to have \Nher stay in Sakura Hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.06,0:00:52.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Look after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.99,0:00:54.60,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Sensei, take responsibility for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.60,0:00:56.28,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and take care of her!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:57.68,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting crumbs everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.68,0:00:59.28,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,We're holding this meeting \Nfor you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.28,0:01:01.46,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You got some up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:01.46,Saku-overlap,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,He's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:03.05,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, indeedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.05,0:01:06.50,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so Kanda will \Nbe on Mashiro Duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:08.88,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? Mashiro Duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.23,0:01:08.88,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,It's decided! It's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.65,0:01:12.21,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Akasaka Ryunosuke: I do not have time to waste on your mundane, pointless meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.65,0:01:12.21,SignGreen,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Ryunosuke-sama has logged out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:11.77,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,The dragon agrees too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.70,0:01:14.63,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,It's unanimous. Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.63,0:01:15.87,Saku-main,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Meeting adjourned!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:17.79,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.24,0:01:20.14,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I need to go over to \NNoriko the nurse's place tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:19.22,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:23.08,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What? I can't ignore that! \NAbsolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.17,0:01:26.30,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.28,0:01:28.15,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.22,0:01:30.48,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we can be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.25,0:01:34.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.09,0:01:36.99,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda Sorata will be on Mashiro Duty! You can \Ndo it, kouhai-kun! I'll be supporting you!\N— Secretary Kamiigusa Misaki
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:36.35,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, this is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.95,0:03:10.91,Eptitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,#02 I Drew a Picture
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:16.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Cabbage, cabbage...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.78,0:03:25.43,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda: Mashiro Duty
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:26.43,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.73,0:03:29.19,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,When you sigh, your happiness escapes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:30.03,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:31.10,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Say, "Ah."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:31.10,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:34.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be on Mashiro Duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.35,0:03:38.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm planning to leave \NSakura Hall soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:41.01,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:43.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're asking me why? Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.75,0:03:44.70,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:48.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't believe you're \Ndressed like that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:49.45,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Put some pants on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:51.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to seduce me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.04,0:03:54.10,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki told me you'd \Nlike it more if I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:55.96,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Mashiron!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:56.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.87,0:03:58.66,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea how hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:00.32,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm working to train Shiina?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:03.05,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro-chan said we've got \Nto work hard while we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.32,0:04:03.05,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Imitating Mashiro
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:05.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, gimme a break! I don't \Nhave time for breakfast now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:07.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly, back to your room!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:09.56,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you planning on going \Nto school without underwear?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:12.35,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what about this cabbage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:13.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We'll pick up something \Nfrom the store for breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:16.85,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.20,0:04:17.98,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:20.70,Saku-main,NORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear. Jin-kun, do you have a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.70,0:04:22.58,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,No... What was that? \NI felt a sudden chill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:23.71,Saku-main,NORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.71,0:04:26.10,Saku-main,NORIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Pain, pain, go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.10,0:04:26.91,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:29.56,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This is painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.56,0:04:31.57,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Salads are 380 yen each.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.57,0:04:33.75,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,For the two of us, that's 760 yen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:35.86,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This is tough on my wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:37.17,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata, are you ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:45.76,Saku-main,CLERK,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.20,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:52.06,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Shiina-san? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:54.67,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm eating a baumkuchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.67,0:04:55.35,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:56.52,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:59.68,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,If that's all it took to get off \Nthe hook, we wouldn't need police!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:01.11,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:03.74,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of life have\N you been living up to now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:05.94,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I drew pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:07.36,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:09.99,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I drew pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:14.58,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I drew pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.58,0:05:15.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you say anything else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:17.71,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:20.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.14,0:05:23.20,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.99,0:05:26.38,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:28.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You opened another one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:33.64,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Conveni-Mart
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.87,0:05:33.64,Saku-main,CLERK,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:35.33,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:37.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.18,0:05:38.78,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, don't sweat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:41.07,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You paid for it, so it's all good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:43.07,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:47.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:51.40,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Her name's Shiina Mashiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:54.64,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a second year art student\N who transferred in this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.64,0:05:56.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She's living in Sakura Hall now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:06:00.84,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're living in Sakura Hall together?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:02.95,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You two must be really close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.95,0:06:04.14,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.14,0:06:06.00,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata is my first boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:06.76,Saku-main,BOTH,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:10.68,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean your "first boy"?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:12.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! Hey, Shiina, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.93,0:06:15.14,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad Sorata was my first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:16.59,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.59,0:06:17.17,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Un—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:20.09,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Unclean!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:20.09,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Aoyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.74,0:06:23.59,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,In England, I was surrounded by girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:26.04,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You're the first boy I've \Nbecome friends with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:28.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You should give the context first!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:30.86,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Context? To her, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:33.45,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.74,0:06:40.76,Saku-main,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,All right, time to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.76,0:06:42.79,Saku-main,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get that fried rice roll today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:46.28,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Mayu, your lunch is so adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:46.28,Saku-overlap,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.28,0:06:48.50,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami, have you seen Sorata?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.50,0:06:49.63,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:52.74,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did he do something again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.74,0:06:55.64,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Do? D-D-Do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:55.64,Saku-overlap,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:06:59.99,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.99,0:07:01.90,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you all by yourself at lunchtime?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:03.19,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a pariah now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I could only afford one bread roll.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.51,0:07:07.32,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm filling up on water.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:09.16,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,How sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:11.34,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,All my money went down the \Ndrain buying Shiina snacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:13.65,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, aren't you \NShiina's legal guardian?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.65,0:07:15.33,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Reimburse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:17.03,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I hear you haven't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.03,0:07:18.99,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,turned in your career plan yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.99,0:07:21.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to change the subject won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:21.81,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Shiina is—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.81,0:07:25.34,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Just put that you want \Nto be a pilot or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.34,0:07:26.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What am I, a grade schooler?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:29.22,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You should try to be \Nmore like Kamiigusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:30.17,Sign,TEXT,0000,0000,0000,,Career Plan: Art\NThird Year: Kamiigusa Misaki\N"My future's so bright, I can't even see it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:30.71,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so narrow-minded...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.71,0:07:34.44,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm being ambitious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:33.12,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She's an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.12,0:07:34.85,Saku-overlap,,0000,0000,0000,,An earthling could never act like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:37.06,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Quit whining over nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:38.78,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Just writing the words \N"continuing my education"...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:40.36,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,will put the faculty office at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.36,0:07:41.23,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:45.14,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's only a career plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:47.89,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but watching you makes me think \Nit might actually mean something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:49.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you saying it's \Nmeaningless for most people?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.12,0:07:52.71,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,They must do it to pick out the students...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.71,0:07:55.79,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,who don't write that they're\N "continuing education for the time being."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.79,0:07:58.95,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing you need\N "for the time being" is beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:07:59.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:01.16,Saku-main,CHIHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:08.00,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She managed to change the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:10.26,Saku-main,BOY A,0000,0000,0000,,I got my fried rice roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:11.22,Saku-main,BOY B,0000,0000,0000,,Woohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:15.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She just does whatever she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.08,0:08:19.00,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,My career plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.00,0:08:20.72,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:23.06,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:24.05,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:25.38,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,They're in here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:28.07,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamiigusa-senpai and \NMitaka-senpai's interview!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:33.40,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,That pair of geniuses \Nare childhood friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.77,0:08:34.78,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:38.30,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,"A prodigal high school \Ngirl has appeared," it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:40.45,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,She seems like a run-of-the-mill weirdo,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:42.34,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but she's actually really talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:44.39,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,It's seriously amazing, \Nisn't it? Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.93,0:08:46.79,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:47.75,Saku-main,BOY,0000,0000,0000,,Kanda-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:49.31,Saku-main,BOY,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's here for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:49.75,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:53.09,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:54.17,Saku-main,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:55.01,Saku-main,BOY,0000,0000,0000,,She's really cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:08:59.30,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:01.90,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home on my own today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:02.60,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:04.60,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.87,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But... if I'm not with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.87,0:09:08.32,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,who knows what you'll get into?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.41,0:09:15.45,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.96,0:09:18.32,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. Don't eat any merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:19.73,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.30,0:09:23.84,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the cutie?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.84,0:09:27.12,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go hogging all the \Ngood luck, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:27.12,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:29.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,There's something wrong with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.05,0:09:30.64,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:32.36,Saku-overlap,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,You said it. She's abnormally cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:34.51,Saku-main,MIYAHARA,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, you always get the breaks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:34.51,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:48.47,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Aoyama's definitely \Ngot the wrong idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.55,0:09:52.64,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:57.53,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Ayano, where's your car?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.90,0:09:59.32,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,I took it to get serviced.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:00.60,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Serviced?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.60,0:10:03.20,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be seeing my \Nbeloved baby for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:04.34,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:05.20,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:06.52,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina-san, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:10.06,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Is it hard being so far from \NRita-san in England?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:13.50,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I have Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.85,0:10:15.14,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:15.84,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,A boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:21.10,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,A boy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:22.29,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Ayano.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.03,0:10:26.52,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Conveni-Mart
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.80,0:10:26.52,Saku-main,CLERK,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:32.52,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Welcom—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.90,0:10:34.22,Saku-main,CLERK,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.07,0:10:36.69,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Um, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.23,0:10:40.11,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,In England, I was surrounded by girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:42.53,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata is the first boy \NI've become friends with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:44.41,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wh-What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.69,0:10:47.20,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,In England, I was \Nsurrounded by girls...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:48.83,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant. What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:50.92,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata told me to tell you the context first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.39,0:10:55.85,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding! \NI was just imagining it all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.85,0:10:56.69,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.69,0:10:59.59,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I supposed to say \Nto Kanda-kun tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.91,0:11:03.80,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um... sorry, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.92,0:11:09.20,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Um, you're called Shiina-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.71,0:11:11.80,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want one of those?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:14.66,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:15.73,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to have one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:19.49,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata said I can't unless I pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:20.90,Saku-main,AYANO,0000,0000,0000,,Two baumkuchen, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:23.61,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Ayano.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.61,0:11:24.98,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:29.25,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.07,0:11:33.15,Saku-main,CLERK,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:39.97,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:43.20,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Shiina made it home okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:47.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari. Are you here to greet me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.49,0:11:55.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, having someone like \Nyou is never a bad thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.34,0:12:01.58,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:07.04,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,The Cabbage Road of Honor...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:09.29,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,It's my birthday today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:10.08,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.53,0:12:12.30,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I had a feeling this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.05,0:12:15.04,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I was right to come home early.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:17.68,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,For my birthday last year...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:20.01,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Misaki decorated herself \Nwith whipped cream,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:21.05,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Jin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:22.16,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and waited for me in my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:25.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You have my sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.27,0:12:27.86,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But why cabbage?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:31.03,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know what \Ngoes on in Misaki's head?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:32.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,But you're childhood friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:36.44,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,What I mean is, the\N thought process of a genius...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:38.29,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,is a mystery to ordinary men.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.71,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? If you're an ordinary man,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:42.82,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,what does that make me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.16,0:12:51.33,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:53.59,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of person are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:56.02,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,to make me open this \Ndangerous box by myself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:58.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It probably won't explode, \Nso you'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:13:00.42,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Probably, is it? Probably?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:07.68,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Jin, happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:11.02,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.63,0:13:16.02,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Ow... Misaki-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.61,0:13:16.03,Saku-overlap,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:18.93,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:20.52,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:21.46,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.46,0:13:23.26,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You're tempting me! \NCover up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.26,0:13:25.95,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Jin, you're so shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:28.95,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,After all the effort I took to \Ncelebrate your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.33,0:13:29.37,Saku-overlap,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:30.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave you guys to it now—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:31.91,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:35.75,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,The staff will have to eat \Nthis delicious cabbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:38.09,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,You'll help me, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.09,0:13:39.92,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not part of your staff!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:40.15,Saku-overlap,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.15,0:13:41.13,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:43.58,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:44.84,Saku-overlap,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,No more! Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.87,0:13:51.81,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't waste any more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:55.29,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I need to leave Sakura Hall before...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.29,0:13:58.00,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,my common sense is eaten away...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.92,0:14:06.30,Sign,MAGAZINE,0000,0000,0000,,What's important is the courage not to miss your chance.\N– Fujisawa Kazuki
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:09.98,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that there isn't \Nanything I want to be, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:14.43,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,Following his original theory...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.43,0:14:19.09,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,that programmers must sleep \Neight hours every day,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:22.63,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryunosuke is currently resting \Nin a dreamlike state.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.06,0:14:26.47,Saku-main,MAID,0000,0000,0000,,From: Maid-chan, who \Nwishes she could sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:27.69,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,alongside Ryunosuke-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.33,0:14:31.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Who can be in a dreamlike state \Nin the middle of this ruckus?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.95,0:14:33.93,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Shiina. You're home...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:33.93,Saku-overlap,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.75,0:14:38.56,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:39.77,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Take off your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.97,0:14:46.19,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you naked.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:49.95,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you want to see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.23,0:14:51.91,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I want your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:53.59,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's not an answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:54.95,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Take them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:56.07,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.07,0:14:56.66,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.13,0:15:00.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're asking me why? \NBecause... it's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:01.92,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:04.26,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It's embarrassing for {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.26,0:15:06.06,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Ayano advised me to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.06,0:15:06.80,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Ayano?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.25,0:15:10.01,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Last year, I entered the \NNew Manga Artist Award competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.01,0:15:11.72,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You won... an award?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:12.98,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:15.52,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,But Ayano saw my work,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.52,0:15:17.90,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and said that the art style was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:20.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. An editor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.00,0:15:22.56,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Ayano advised me to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:25.02,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're starting from there again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.62,0:15:27.92,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,She said, if delicate expressions of emotion...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:29.78,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,are difficult for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.91,0:15:33.69,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,then why don't you try \Nmore extreme depictions?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:37.63,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.51,0:15:41.93,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you want \Nto see a naked man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.44,0:15:45.96,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shojo manga can be \Npretty extreme sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:48.48,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,If I take my clothes off, \Nwill you take off yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:50.38,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.38,0:15:51.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll take off my clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.67,0:15:53.27,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You just want me to \Ntake them off, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:54.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I won't take off my underwear, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.99,0:15:56.01,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's my only condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.31,0:15:57.72,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I will take off your underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:16:00.02,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You're crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:15.15,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:19.12,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:25.39,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It feels hard and heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.27,0:16:35.71,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Your heart is beating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.71,0:16:37.22,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.00,0:16:40.27,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Your pulse is quickening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:42.35,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Whose fault is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:43.34,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:44.40,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.04,0:16:45.70,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Hold me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.70,0:16:46.65,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:51.73,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,More.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.10,0:16:55.10,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:56.36,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.36,0:16:57.78,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Have you had sex?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:00.79,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Sorata?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:03.11,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't surprise me like that! \NNo, I haven't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:04.26,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,But you have a nice body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.26,0:17:05.67,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of reasoning is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:08.85,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,My body's only like \Nthis because I played soccer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.85,0:17:10.81,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,in grade school and middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.81,0:17:11.66,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,What about now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.66,0:17:12.72,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't play anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:14.42,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell just by watching me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:16.13,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:19.85,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of reasons \Nto quit other than an injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:22.35,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:28.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.78,0:17:31.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't particularly good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:34.51,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I kept at it for nine years,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:36.75,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess you could \Nsay I saw my limitations...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:40.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's why I lost my passion for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.54,0:17:44.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,There came a point where I stopped\N  caring whether we lost or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.17,0:17:46.96,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and I subconsciously learned \Nnot to try so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:49.71,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,It happens all the time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:53.47,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:57.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Shiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:05.77,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Am I supposed to just \Nsit here like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:08.73,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.01,0:18:18.74,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's not interesting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:20.58,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:21.99,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Ayano told me it wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:26.00,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,You can get rid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:27.39,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:29.29,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'll redraw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:31.90,Sign,PAPER,0000,0000,0000,,New Manga Artist Award Entry Requirements
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.66,0:18:31.25,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Redraw it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:34.55,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to apply for \Nthe new artist award again?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:42.55,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You must really like drawing manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:49.14,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put your clothes on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:49.98,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.79,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:52.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:54.57,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What more do you have planned for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:56.28,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you sleep tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.28,0:18:59.05,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Try to sound a little \Nsexier when you say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:19:00.49,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you sleep tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:02.36,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That sounded exactly the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:09.00,Sign,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.99,0:19:12.92,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:14.88,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,You sure had fun last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.88,0:19:16.42,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have fun at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.42,0:19:21.18,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, did you manage to get \NJin-san to eat that cabbage?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.49,0:19:24.78,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you choose \Nto ask about, kouhai-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:27.88,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... I'll go take out the garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:36.15,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand \Ntheir relationship...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.88,0:19:41.03,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're early.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.03,0:19:41.99,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you on your way to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:45.45,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah. Good work today, Kanda-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:47.58,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're not angry anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:50.29,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I-I wasn't angry in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:52.43,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But... Aoyama, you speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:53.79,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,in Kansai dialect when you're angry, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:57.01,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I just told you I ain't angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:02.80,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,That girl I met yesterday is \Npretty weird, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:04.26,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,She's an art student, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.26,0:20:05.54,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Shiina?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:08.78,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she wants to be a manga artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.78,0:20:11.64,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She's good at drawing, \Nbut her work's a little strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:13.88,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She works hard, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:16.31,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could say...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.31,0:20:18.29,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,she makes me want to cheer her on...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.63,0:20:20.19,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Same goes for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:23.16,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Working so early in the morning so \Nyou can become a voice actor...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:24.21,Saku-main,,0000,0000,0000,,is pretty amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.21,0:20:25.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I respect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.48,0:20:28.30,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, anyway, I've got to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.30,0:20:29.48,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,See you at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.48,0:20:30.29,Saku-main,NANAMI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:35.17,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,They really are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:38.66,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Both Aoyama and Shiina.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.66,0:20:40.95,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,They've both found something \Nthey can be absorbed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.69,0:20:48.59,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,I might not be as good as Misaki-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.59,0:20:50.88,Saku-thought,,0000,0000,0000,,and the others, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:56.30,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I wonder if I'll be able \Nto find something someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.14,0:20:59.44,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She left her stuff out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:05.55,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,That's a beautiful drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.55,0:21:06.57,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.01,0:21:10.29,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you thanking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:11.72,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Because I drew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.72,0:21:12.29,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.29,0:21:15.36,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,What? You mean you didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.36,0:21:16.38,Saku-main,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Jin-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.38,0:21:17.89,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.58,0:21:28.55,Saku-thought,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro-chan must not have told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.94,0:21:32.68,Saku-thought,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you must've at least seen \Nher face on TV or in magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:32.69,Sign,SEARCH,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina Mashiro
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.28,0:21:35.44,Saku-thought,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Shiina Mashiro is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.79,0:21:43.88,Sign,SEARCH,0000,0000,0000,,"Special Exhibition: Contemporary Artist, Shiina Mashiro"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.79,0:21:43.88,Sign,SEARCH,0000,0000,0000,,"The prodigal girl who has descended\N upon the world of contemporary art..."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.34,0:21:49.99,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,"Something she can be absorbed in?" \NWhat was I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.66,0:21:53.73,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't on Misaki-senpai \Nor Jin-san's level.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.46,0:21:55.87,Saku-thought,SORATA,0000,0000,0000,,Shiina is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.31,0:23:23.11,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Suffer more, little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.84,0:23:26.10,Saku-main,JIN,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro-chan, come eat some—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.79,0:23:27.78,Saku-main,MASHIRO,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.72,0:23:33.20,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Cabbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.20,0:23:35.42,Saku-main,MISAKI,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm going to give away the ribbon....
